name: PRE-ORDER: Limited Edition Killa Bee G.A.S. Mask "Classic" Tee
description:
Keep the buzz in this made to order tee by Freehand Profit.

LIMITED EDITION tees will only be offered through Pre-Orders from now on. Orders will be open until midnight 10/1. All shirts will ship week no later than 10/8 (Orders placed sooner will be received sooner as all garments are made to order - meaning it gets printed when you order it).

Each tee will be printed as it's ordered using the latest and greatest Direct To Garment Printing by Imprint Revolution. This allows for unlimited colors and provides a high quality print that is soft to the touch. Freehand Profit came to know and love this print process while working for Imprint Revolution.

Made to order/direct to garment printed tees will be printed on 100% cotton American Apparel tees made right here in LA.

PROFITink.com no longer offers international shipping. All orders must be shipped within the US. Sorry guys, just had to much hassle in the past getting my work through customs.

description:

name: Army of the Undeadstock (ART BOOK)
description:
"Army of the Undeadstock" released 11.28.12! The book features more than 250 pages of full color photographs showcasing nearly every sneaker mask I've created over the course of the past few years. Each mask (more than 30 total) is accompanied by a custom crafted haiku written by San Diego poet B(e) Selah. The book features 2 forwards, one by Woody (editor of Sneaker Freaker) representing the sneaker community and one by Noah Scalin (creator of Skull-A-Day) representing the art world. 

This is Freehand Profit's first book, get this 1st Edition now before it's too late!

Available in 2 shipping options (COST OF SHIPPING INCLUDED):

 $5 in a standard envelope (Standard Delivery)
